{"tid":514152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★來港住劏房，公屋冇回音----蝗婦叫苦 ：我福建住4,000呎別墅 !!","createTime":"2017-12-30T09:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T16:46:29.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b41beb4c6e812c01aa021ddb0e9b28a4e9faf7f1","tid":514152,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:24:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「我在福建住4000呎別墅，這裏比我家保姆房還要小！</span>」劏房戶中不乏新移民家庭，24歲福建女嫁來香港後，竟發現一家三口要擠在180呎劏房，但為了3歲兒子日後在港接受教育，只好忍下去。<br />\n<br />\n24歲的湯太與同齡的港男4年前結婚，二人原本在內地生活，生活屬於中上，但隨著3歲兒子長大，需入讀幼稚園，兩年前，一家三口搬回香港，現時任職水電工程的丈夫月入約1.7萬元，結婚時<span style=\"color: red;\">已申請公屋，但未有回音</span>。兩年前搬來港，惟有以月租4,800元租住180呎劏房，今年10月業主更加租至5,000元，湯太形容這裏十分壓迫：「有時我也頂唔住返回內地。」現時持雙程證來港的她，一想到日後兒子在港可接受良好教育，惟有繼續忍下去，目前只盼望公屋盡快獲批，改善居住環境。<br />\n<br />\n原本住在台山的譚太跟丈夫結婚10多年，與14歲兒子一家三口亦一直在內地生活，但丈夫近年因要照顧日漸年老的居港父親，遂搬來港租住劏房，兩房一廳面積約200呎，月租8,000元，現時只有譚生及其父親居住，稍後倘譚母以及譚太母子三人獲批單程證來港，屆時該劏房便要住上5人，譚太指：「以前在大陸睇電視，好少睇到香港有啲咁嘅屋，依家親眼見過住過，真係嚇一跳。」她又指，在台山住的祖屋<span style=\"color: red;\">「一間房都大過呢度」</span>，但嫁雞隨雞，即使住劏房，她也要接受。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171230/large/1514564379_901b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171230%2Flarge%2F1514564379_901b.jpg&h=ea21e1a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171230/57642606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F57642606&d=K2ZWUtMstStDIes0vZ4PKjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b5613d4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171230%2F57642606&h=339d1b43\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20171230/57642606</a>"},{"pid":"f7ab6fd9bc9014f4309c77c1a6732eda553dad4f","tid":514152,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26abacd39ba8166a98fe4d6ee5da80c9935e9815","tid":514152,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:25:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171230/large/1514564381_3e23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171230%2Flarge%2F1514564381_3e23.jpg&h=fb255c2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28baa8ed88dac3bcd51684c17bf064386d70005b","tid":514152,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好慘好委屈佢"},{"pid":"a418aa195532a5a70ac4099fa9ad197b034e370d","tid":514152,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:27:25.000Z","msg":"願意資助十蚊比佢返鄉下"},{"pid":"31152a00a33223bec405b658a449f7e6e9e096c6","tid":514152,"uid":106375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:27:56.000Z","msg":"賣左福建幢樓佢租間大啲既屋囉"},{"pid":"b1b7ba24599ad29e4b0a768bf60931b3f16fd97b","tid":514152,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28baa8ed88dac3bcd51684c17bf064386d70005b","tid":514152,"uid":90,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:26:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好慘好委屈佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T09:30:11.000Z","msg":"勵志"},{"pid":"2d65faecc03eba77dfe192b1d110ad365b7ca280","tid":514152,